General.Name: Aman Agrindo
General.Description: PT Aman Agrindo Tbk engages in the plantation of sugarcane and trading of sugar in Indonesia. It offers granulated, liquid, and brown sugar products. The company is also involved in the wholesale and retail of food and other beverages, tobacco, agricultural products, live animals, beverage ingredients, and food commodities, as well as vegetable, fruit, and tuber farming. PT Aman Agrindo Tbk was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Semarang, Indonesia.
General.Address: Ruko Bangkong Plaza C-10, Semarang, Indonesia, 50242
